==English==

===Noun===
'''[[superessive]] [[case]]'''

#{{grammar}}: noun [[case]] used to indicate location '''on''' a surface. In English, it roughly corresponds to the prepositions "on" or "on top of," as in "on top of the house." [[Hungarian]] is a language that uses the superessive case.

